  - name: About This Dashboard
    type: text
    title_text: About This Dashboard
    body_text: |-
      This dashboard is an enhanced version of the ecommerce dashboards [1) Business Pulse - Basic](/dashboards/1) and [2) Business Pulse - Intermediate](/dashboards/2).

      This dashboard adds these features:
      <br>- User Lifetime Revenue Rank and Item Count Group made available
      <br>- Breakdowns based on <span style="color: green;" >High Priority Item</span> designation

      <details><summary>
      + Other notes</summary>
      - This Dashboard shows only Valid items (Items that were not cancelled or returned)
      <br>- ‘New Users’ only counts users with any valid orders meeting the filter criteria.
      <br>- INTERACTIVITY REMINDER: Click field values to drill down to more detail.
      <br><br>
      </details>
    row: 0
    col: 0
    width: 15
    height: 4
    tab_name: ''
